<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">会上，党总支书记蔡平对调研小组一行的到来表示热烈的欢迎，并对校党委组织部在学院党建工作中多年来的关心和帮助表示感谢。对学院贯彻落实校党委党建工作部署情况、党建工作创新和品牌特色建设、基层组织建设、党员干部队伍教育培养等工作进行了介绍。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2n18Qa8gmEJ1icacXhYic7ryibPE55GtgS15q9BJUImjWvic1WszIyBSvXPmuEticHa15pcDkxB2U0eHSErjUDibXaCA/640?wx_fmt=png&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="210" height="229" style="width: 210px; height: 229px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">随后，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: transparent; caret-color: red;">程杨胜部长对我院基层党建工作给予肯定，随即调度了学院党总支基层党建“三化”建设、抓好思想政治教育和德育工作、意识形态工作的有关情况等，并对打造学院党建品牌、推动统战工作发展等方面提出了具体指导意见，就学院提出的主要困难提出建议。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">调研小组对照督查清单，以现场看点、查看资料、询问交流等方式，逐条对经济管理学院党总支党建工作完成情况进行检查，确保将相关工作查细、查实、查准。着重对“三会一课”以及当前重点工作开展情况、党建资料是否规范化运转等情况进行检查。</span></p>